    <node id="Kenosha">
      <data key="d0">Kenosha</data>
      <data key="d1">location</data>
      <data key="d2">Kenosha is a city located in Wisconsin that functions as both a residential center and a significant mailing address hub for numerous individuals, property owners, and business contacts. The city serves as the official mailing and residential address for a diverse population of residents and professionals engaged in various activities, including real estate transactions and commercial operations.

Among the many residents and contacts associated with Kenosha are Juan Lopez, Jose Lozada, Gary Orvis, Kim Sandberg, Beatriz Ayala, Kamal Echcharrady, Michael Morrone, Tanya Patterson, Carlos Chavez, Adam Spears, James Wichert, Adam Martin, Soto, Dean Van Brunt, and Dean Greve. The city is particularly notable as a mailing city for multiple seller contacts and individuals utilizing addresses within its jurisdiction for correspondence and official documentation purposes.

Kenosha's significance extends to its role in real estate infrastructure, with various property owners maintaining residences and business addresses throughout the city. Specific properties, such as that located at 5106 21st Ave, represent examples of the real estate holdings within Kenosha. The city's comprehensive address infrastructure supports personal, commercial, and administrative needs for its population of residents and business contacts.

Overall, Kenosha operates as an important municipality within Wisconsin's administrative and commercial landscape, accommodating a diverse array of individuals and organizations who rely on the city's address system for their personal and professional correspondence needs.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-1586e3be1fdda26b39569d82162119b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0140fd3b1127c271fade621f8b31cec8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74378d8355e556d02ba5b6466c49dd84&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-62ad05910b665edcdcec39264a9a2ed3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-570bb79cebc263e4858f0465fb382b94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1742d1f0b47241be836c6f6cf2834be8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bac957d207c7b94aed19fda9c59453c0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc9c8892db76489f775e4bafba3b4573&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a1e36649b6695df81836ffc82945701&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f909e947c1e458ba8b0cf736ae82fd4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-86ab94e7e456fc30f252af8a6ff7740c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9f78473811a1bbb7d28a0046e4915688&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bcaf6fc79740f57a8a16575bee5e9955&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a75bdc0bb8e8445a0a78c75dd2798032&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3418c246caa4f1264e1ac2c0d0d0290c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ebc17f08d578247874158c41bf95964&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2dcec5bbd52bc4512a40342f1bfde243</data>
