    <node id="Wisconsin">
      <data key="d0">Wisconsin</data>
      <data key="d1">location</data>
      <data key="d2">Wisconsin is a state in the United States that serves as the primary geographic center and jurisdiction for multiple properties, contacts, and business activities. The state functions as a unified location where all listed properties referenced in the dataset are distributed and situated.

Wisconsin is home to all identified seller contacts documented in the records, including Juan Lopez, Soto, Kathryn Knutson, and Antonia Guilani. These contacts are integral to the business operations and property transactions that occur within the state. All contacts maintain mail addresses associated with their respective property locations within Wisconsin's territory, establishing the state as the central hub for property ownership and contact management.

Notably, Antonia Guilani is documented as owning property in Wisconsin and is represented in the contact records maintained for the state. The comprehensive dataset demonstrates that Wisconsin encompasses all listed properties and their corresponding contacts, consolidating all real estate holdings and associated contact information within a single jurisdiction.</data>
