    <node id="Pinnacle Group Wisconsin">
      <data key="d0">Pinnacle Group Wisconsin</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">Pinnacle Group Wisconsin is a real estate organization that operates an integrated contact management and property management system. The organization hosts and manages several digital tools designed to facilitate real estate operations and client engagement. These tools include a Property Inspector tool, property inspection capabilities, and client invite and management features. The organization operates these systems through its web platform at pinnaclegroupwi.com, where clients and contacts can access the contact management system along with property inspection and client management tools. Pinnacle Group Wisconsin's infrastructure supports property management workflows by combining contact management, property inspection, and client relationship management functions into a unified platform.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-0140fd3b1127c271fade621f8b31cec8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-62ad05910b665edcdcec39264a9a2ed3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc9c8892db76489f775e4bafba3b4573&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a0c430a64acf1cfdadb5b23dd9f17d27&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3418c246caa4f1264e1ac2c0d0d0290c</data>
