    <node id="Alex Bot">
      <data key="d0">Alex Bot</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Alex Bot is a bot system being developed with multiple agents including El Secretario and El Planificador for email monitoring and calendar management.&lt;SEP&gt;Alex Bot is a Python-based automation bot (`alex_bot.py`) that updates field mappings and writes directly to Airtable with operational tools.&lt;SEP&gt;Alex Bot is an automated service that executes tasks from task_queue.json and memoria_ALex.md, with restart completed after API Key configuration.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-275ab3ea07b35b11481b16e0c66c1a8e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8315e5960fc142d25fda2af73ac1a1be&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-282facf0c5627ccef9f138a7f4d13fbb</data>
