    <node id="El Planificador">
      <data key="d0">El Planificador</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">El Planificador is a calendar management agent that is 95% operational and requires OAuth configuration for Google Calendar integration.&lt;SEP&gt;El Planificador is a Google Calendar Agent component of Alex Bot that is 95% complete and requires credentials.json for full installation.&lt;SEP&gt;A system component mentioned in the changelog title that is referenced but not detailed in the provided text.&lt;SEP&gt;El Planificador is a Google Calendar management system that provides daily summaries, reminders, and scheduling capabilities through Telegram commands.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-275ab3ea07b35b11481b16e0c66c1a8e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-63ef4572aaf7092b6af41d899303a0d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb3c6f1b4d44514dab8d8aa921011d3f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-68fbc7d74cbf3c49b18474190843517e</data>
