      <data key="d0">Jorge</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Jorge is the individual who provided OAuth credentials from Google Cloud Console for the Pinnacle ALEX Bot project.&lt;SEP&gt;Jorge is responsible for executing the Google OAuth authorization script (python3 secretario/auth_google.py) via SSH.&lt;SEP&gt;Jorge is a team member responsible for manual fixes in Airtable UI, approving tasks, and managing leads in the Airtable RE table.&lt;SEP&gt;Jorge is a person who approved critical tasks including the installation of Blotato MCP on the VPS.</data>
