    <node id="Tracerfy">
      <data key="d0">Tracerfy</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">Tracerfy is a data sourcing organization that provides skip trace services and functions as a lead generation platform. The company specializes in identifying and tracing property sellers and potential property owners by collecting, organizing, and maintaining comprehensive databases of skip trace data. Through its operations as a lead source provider, Tracerfy supplies contact information and lead generation data to clients who utilize the information for business development, prospecting activities, and outreach in the real estate market.

Tracerfy's core function involves tracing specific individuals' contact details and facilitating direct contact between clients and potential leads. The organization serves as an external service provider that enables clients to reach out to and engage with property owners and sellers identified through its skip trace systems. The company maintains structured data management practices, including the automatic archival of email communications after 30 days of deletion, demonstrating institutional protocols for information handling and retention.&lt;SEP&gt;An external email sender from which all emails are automatically archived silently without notifying Telegram, Airtable, or Claude.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-74378d8355e556d02ba5b6466c49dd84&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc9c8892db76489f775e4bafba3b4573&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-90e6e1bf3650213000b0b51a4246a3a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a75bdc0bb8e8445a0a78c75dd2798032&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47d5f8782d66ff14f9321d979ddb10a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ebc17f08d578247874158c41bf95964&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2dcec5bbd52bc4512a40342f1bfde243&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-275ab3ea07b35b11481b16e0c66c1a8e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-68fbc7d74cbf3c49b18474190843517e</data>
