      <data key="d1">location</data>
      <data key="d2">Green Bay is a city in Wisconsin that serves as a residential and contact hub for multiple individuals. The city is home to several notable residents and contacts, including Jason Smith, who maintains an address at 2817 Timber Ln, WI 54313, and Ryan M Dempsey, identified as a lead contact in the area. Additional residents of Green Bay include Maricela Delcampo, whose mailing address is based in the city; Tina Hernandez; Susan Sajec; Austin Bretzel; Donna Peterson; Kathryn Knutson; and Thomas Baker. Green Bay functions as a central location for contact information and residential addresses for this diverse group of individuals.</data>
