    <node id="VPS">
      <data key="d0">VPS</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">VPS is a virtual private server running Claude Code as root and hosting automated agents for email and calendar management.&lt;SEP&gt;VPS is the virtual private server where Alex Bot components are deployed and running, located at /opt/alex-bot/.&lt;SEP&gt;Virtual Private Server at IP 187.77.215.146 hosts the Telegram bot and related services.&lt;SEP&gt;VPS is a virtual private server at `/opt/alex-bot/` hosting the automation system and configuration files.&lt;SEP&gt;VPS is a virtual private server where the Blotato MCP server needs to be installed.</data>
