    <node id="Gemma Marshall">
      <data key="d0">Gemma Marshall</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Gemma Marshall is a seller contact categorized at the New stage who represents an Instagram growth agency specializing in social media services. Contact information for Gemma Marshall includes the primary phone number 4855157885 and email address gemmamarshall811@gmail.com.

Gemma Marshall initiated contact through a website form submission, during which negotiation notes were provided regarding Instagram account growth services. The agency represented by Gemma Marshall offers follower growth services without utilizing bots, positioning itself as a hands-on social media operation. The primary focus of the agency is to help clients build Instagram authority and expand their audience through organic growth strategies.

The lead source for this contact is documented as originating from a Website Form submission, and Gemma Marshall's current status within the sales pipeline is classified as New, indicating an early-stage business development opportunity.</data>
