    <node id="Pinnacle Group">
      <data key="d0">Pinnacle Group</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">Pinnacle Group is an organization that operates a comprehensive digital platform centered on property inspection and client management services. The organization maintains an official website at pinnaclegroupwi.com, which serves as the primary interface for its core operations and client engagement.

The organization's primary operational tools include a Property Inspector tool designed for efficient property assessment and documentation, and a sophisticated client management system that facilitates the organization and tracking of client contacts and property information through a centralized database. These systems work in conjunction to streamline property-related workflows and enable comprehensive record management for the organization's clients.

Pinnacle Group also operates client invitation tools designed to enhance communication and engagement with its clientele. The digital infrastructure supports various business functions, including inquiry management and service promotion. The organization has engaged with inquiries regarding video advertising services, indicating its use of website and contact systems for business development purposes.

The organization is associated with the business email address deals@pinnaclegroupwi.com and operates a Google Cloud project identified as pinnacle-alex. These digital assets support the organization's administrative and technical operations, ensuring reliable access to its property inspection and client management capabilities for both internal operations and external client interactions.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-74378d8355e556d02ba5b6466c49dd84&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-241acf4604830fbe81c295e7f9c6a7d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1742d1f0b47241be836c6f6cf2834be8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a1e36649b6695df81836ffc82945701&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-86ab94e7e456fc30f252af8a6ff7740c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f90775d3d3e87f44c5faf72432843252&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a75bdc0bb8e8445a0a78c75dd2798032&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47d5f8782d66ff14f9321d979ddb10a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb3c6f1b4d44514dab8d8aa921011d3f</data>
