    <node id="Website Form">
      <data key="d0">Website Form</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Website Form is a lead source method used to capture and acquire new contacts through a website-based submission process. This channel enables potential sellers and seller prospects to submit contact information, inquiries, and negotiation notes directly via the website. Several contacts have been acquired through Website Form submissions, including Gemma Marshall, Simone Houchens, and Joanna Riggs, each of whom provided their contact information through this lead source method. Website Form functions as an automated or semi-automated channel that streamlines the initial contact acquisition process by allowing prospects to reach out with their information and questions without requiring direct outbound prospecting efforts.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-8a1e36649b6695df81836ffc82945701&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f909e947c1e458ba8b0cf736ae82fd4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bcaf6fc79740f57a8a16575bee5e9955&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f90775d3d3e87f44c5faf72432843252&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3418c246caa4f1264e1ac2c0d0d0290c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2dcec5bbd52bc4512a40342f1bfde243</data>
